name: Work 00001 mountain landscape digital impressionist
description: This is the first work I published on my journey into digital art, falling in love with things that can be done with Corel Painter and a reference image. It uses digital watercolor on virtual canvas I created from watercolor paper photographs I took. The reference image is a mountain view, photographed from an iPhone of all things.
